                html: `If the wall is already damaged and you also want to avoid visible finish errors after the repair, our guide on <a href="/blog/mistakes-to-avoid-when-patching-drywall/" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline">mistakes to avoid when patching drywall</a> is a useful second read.`,
